 ISO C++ 200x, e.g., identifiers in ISO C++ 1998 that will become keywords
-in ISO C++ 200x.  This warning is enabled by @option{-Wall}.
+in ISO C++ 200x.  This warning turns on @option{-Wnarrowing} and is
